msgstr "Argumenti uslova moraju imati iste dimenzije."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The array of ranges containing the values to be counted."
msgstr "Niz opsega koji sadrže vrijednosti za prebrojavanje."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The array or range containing dependent (y) values that are already known, "
"used to curve fit an ideal exponential growth curve."
msgstr ""
"Niz ili opseg koji sadrži zavisne (y) vrijednosti koje su već poznate, "
"koristi se za podešavanje krive idealnog eksponencijalnog rasta."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The array or range containing dependent (y) values that are already known, "
"used to curve fit an ideal linear trend."
msgstr ""
"Niz ili opseg koji sadrži zavisne (y) vrijednosti koje su već poznate, "
"koristi se za podešavanje krive idealnog linearnog trenda."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The array or range containing the data to consider, structured in such a way"
" that the first row contains the labels for each column's values."
msgstr ""
"Niz ili opseg koji sadrži podatke za razmatranje, strukturirano tako da prvi"
" red sadrži oznake za vrijednosti svake kolone."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The array or range containing the dataset to consider."
msgstr "Niz ili opseg koji sadrži skup podataka za razmatranje."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The array or range of values that will be reduced by corresponding entries "
"in array_y, squared, and added together."
msgstr ""
"Niz ili opseg vrijednosti koji će biti smanjene odgovarajućim unosima u "
"array_y, kvadriranim i sabranim."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The array or range of values that will be subtracted from corresponding "
"entries in array_x, the result squared, and all such results added together."
msgstr ""
"Niz ili opseg vrijednosti koje će biti oduzete od odgovarajućih unosa u "
"array_x, rezultat kvadriran, i svi takvi rezultati sabrani."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The array or range of values whose squares will be added to the squares of "
"corresponding entries in array_x and added together."
msgstr ""
"Niz ili opseg vrijednosti čiji će kvadrati biti dodati kvadratima "
"odgovarajućih unosa u array_x i sabrani."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The array or range of values whose squares will be added to the squares of "
"corresponding entries in array_y and added together."
msgstr ""
"Niz ili opseg vrijednosti čiji će kvadrati biti dodati kvadratima "
"odgovarajućih unosa u array_y i sabrani."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The array or range of values whose squares will be reduced by the squares of"
" corresponding entries in array_y and added together."
msgstr ""
"Niz ili opseg vrijednosti čiji će kvadrati biti smanjeni kvadratima "
"odgovarajućih unosa u array_y i sabrani."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The array or range of values whose squares will be subtracted from the "
"squares of corresponding entries in array_x and added together."
msgstr ""
"Niz ili opseg vrijednosti čiji će kvadrati biti oduzeti od kvadrata "
"odgovarajućih unosa u array_x i sabrani."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The array that contains the columns to be returned."
msgstr "Niz koji sadrži kolone koje se vraćaju."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The array that contains the rows to be returned."
msgstr "Niz koji sadrži redove koji se vraćaju."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The array to expand."
msgstr "Niz za proširenje."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The array which will be transformed."
msgstr "Niz koji će biti transformisan."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The base of the logarithm."
msgstr "Baza logaritma."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The base to convert the value from."
msgstr "Baza iz koje se konvertuje vrijednost."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The case-sensitive format of the result, enclosed in quotation marks. "
"Examples: \"0.00\" rounded to 2 decimal places, \"hh:mm:ss\" for "
"hour:minutes:seconds."
msgstr ""
"Format rezultata koji razlikuje velika i mala slova, u navodnicima. "
"Primjeri: \"0.00\" zaokruženo na 2 decimale, \"hh:mm:ss\" za "
"sat:minute:sekunde."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The case_sensitivity (%s) must be 0 or 1."
msgstr "case_sensitivity (%s) mora biti 0 ili 1."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The cell whose column number will be returned. Column A corresponds to 1. By"
" default, the function use the cell in which the formula is entered."
msgstr ""
"Ćelija čiji se broj kolone vraća. Kolona A odgovara 1. Po zadanim "
"postavkama, funkcija koristi ćeliju u kojoj je unesena formula."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The cell whose row number will be returned. By default, this function uses "
"the cell in which the formula is entered."
msgstr ""
"Ćelija čiji se broj reda vraća. Po zadanim postavkama, ova funkcija koristi "
"ćeliju u kojoj je unesena formula."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The character or characters to use to split text."
msgstr "Znak ili znakovi koji se koriste za dijeljenje teksta."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The column index of the value to be returned, where the first column in "
"range is numbered 1."
msgstr ""
"Indeks kolone vrijednosti koja se vraća, gdje je prva kolona u opsegu "
"numerisana 1."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The column number (not name) of the cell reference. A is column number 1. "
msgstr "Broj kolone (ne naziv) reference ćelije. A je kolona broj 1. "

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The columns argument (%s) must be strictly positive."
msgstr "Argument columns (%s) mora biti strogo pozitivan."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The columns arguments (%s) must be greater or equal than the number of "
"columns of the array."
msgstr ""
"Argumenti columns (%s) moraju biti veći ili jednaki broju kolona niza."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The columns arguments must be between -%s and %s (got %s), excluding 0."
msgstr ""
"Argumenti columns moraju biti između -%s i %s (dobiveno %s), isključujući 0."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The columns indexes of the columns to be returned."
msgstr "Indeksi kolona koje se vraćaju."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/currency/formulas.js:0
msgid "The company to take the exchange rate from."
msgstr "Kompanija od koje se uzima kurs."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The corresponding value to be returned if case1 matches expression."
msgstr "Odgovarajuća vrijednost koja se vraća ako case1 odgovara izrazu."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The current value of the annuity."
msgstr "Trenutna vrijednost anuiteta."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The data points to return the y values for on the ideal curve fit."
msgstr ""
"Tačke podataka za koje se vraćaju y vrijednosti na idealnom podešavanju "
"krive."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The data to be filtered."
msgstr "Podaci koji se filtriraju."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The data to be sorted."
msgstr "Podaci za sortiranje."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The data to filter by unique entries."
msgstr "Podaci za filtriranje prema jedinstvenim unosima."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The data view makes the carousel transparent, revealing the data underneath."
msgstr ""
"Prikaz podataka čini karusel transparentnim, otkrivajući podatke ispod."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The data you entered in %s violates the data validation rule set on the cell:\n"
"%s"
msgstr ""
"Podaci koje ste unijeli u %s krše pravilo validacije podataka postavljeno na ćeliji:\n"
"%s"

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The date for which to determine the ISO week number. Must be a reference to "
"a cell containing a date, a function returning a date type, or a number."
msgstr ""
"Datum za koji se određuje ISO broj sedmice. Mora biti referenca na ćeliju "
"koja sadrži datum, funkciju koja vraća datumski tip, ili broj."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The date for which to determine the day of the week. Must be a reference to "
"a cell containing a date, a function returning a date type, or a number."
msgstr ""
"Datum za koji se određuje dan u sedmici. Mora biti referenca na ćeliju koja "
"sadrži datum, funkciju koja vraća datumski tip, ili broj."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The date for which to determine the week number. Must be a reference to a "
"cell containing a date, a function returning a date type, or a number."
msgstr ""
"Datum za koji se određuje broj sedmice. Mora biti referenca na ćeliju koja "
"sadrži datum, funkciju koja vraća datumski tip, ili broj."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The date from which to begin counting."
msgstr "Datum od kojeg počinje brojanje."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The date from which to calculate the end of quarter."
msgstr "Datum od kojeg se računa kraj kvartala."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The date from which to calculate the end of the year."
msgstr "Datum od kojeg se računa kraj godine."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The date from which to calculate the result."
msgstr "Datum od kojeg se računa rezultat."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The date from which to calculate the start of quarter."
msgstr "Datum od kojeg se računa početak kvartala."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The date from which to calculate the start of the year."
msgstr "Datum od kojeg se računa početak godine."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The date from which to extract the day."
msgstr "Datum iz kojeg se izdvaja dan."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The date from which to extract the month."
msgstr "Datum iz kojeg se izdvaja mjesec."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The date from which to extract the quarter."
msgstr "Datum iz kojeg se izdvaja kvartal."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The date from which to extract the year."
msgstr "Datum iz kojeg se izdvaja godina."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The date the asset was purchased."
msgstr "Datum kupovine sredstva."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The date the first period ended."
msgstr "Datum završetka prvog perioda."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The date the security was initially issued."
msgstr "Datum kada je hartija od vrijednosti prvobitno izdata."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The day component of the date."
msgstr "Komponenta dana datuma."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The delimiter (%s) must be not be empty."
msgstr "Graničnik (%s) ne smije biti prazan."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The delimiters cannot be empty values."
msgstr "Graničnici ne mogu biti prazne vrijednosti."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The deprecation rate."
msgstr "Stopa amortizacije."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The desired instance of the delimiter after which we extract the text. A "
"negative number searches from the end."
msgstr ""
"Željena instanca graničnika nakon kojeg izdvajamo tekst. Negativan broj "
"pretražuje od kraja."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The desired instance of the delimiter before which we extract the text. A "
"negative number searches from the end."
msgstr ""
"Željena instanca graničnika prije kojeg izdvajamo tekst. Negativan broj "
"pretražuje od kraja."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The discount rate of the bill at time of purchase."
msgstr "Diskontna stopa mjenice u trenutku kupovine."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The discount rate of the investment over one period."
msgstr "Diskontna stopa investicije za jedan period."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The discount rate of the security at time of purchase."
msgstr "Diskontna stopa hartije od vrijednosti u trenutku kupovine."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The discount rate of the security invested in."
msgstr "Diskontna stopa hartije od vrijednosti u koju se investira."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The divisor must be different from zero."
msgstr "Djelilac mora biti različit od nule."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The effective interest rate per year."
msgstr "Efektivna kamatna stopa godišnje."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The effective_rate (%s) must be strictly positive."
msgstr "effective_rate (%s) mora biti strogo pozitivna."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The end date of the period from which to calculate the number of net working"
" days."
msgstr "Krajnji datum perioda iz kojeg se izračunava broj neto radnih dana."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The end date to consider in the calculation."
msgstr "Krajnji datum za razmatranje u izračunu."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The end date to consider in the calculation. Must be a reference to a cell "
"containing a DATE, a function returning a DATE type, or a number."
msgstr ""
"Krajnji datum za razmatranje u izračunu. Mora biti referenca na ćeliju koja "
"sadrži DATE, funkciju koja vraća DATE tip, ili broj."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The end date to consider in the calculation. Must be a reference to a cell "
"containing a date, a function returning a date type, or a number."
msgstr ""
"Krajnji datum za razmatranje u izračunu. Mora biti referenca na ćeliju koja "
"sadrži datum, funkciju koja vraća datumski tip, ili broj."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The end of the date range."
msgstr "Kraj opsega datuma."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The end_period (%(end)s) must be smaller or equal to the life (%(life)s)."
msgstr "end_period (%(end)s) mora biti manji ili jednak vijeku (%(life)s)."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The end_period (%s) must be positive or null."
msgstr "end_period (%s) mora biti pozitivan ili null."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The expected annual yield of the security."
msgstr "Očekivani godišnji prinos hartije od vrijednosti."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The exponent to raise e."
msgstr "Eksponent na koji se diže e."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The extract_length argument (%s) must be positive or null."
msgstr "Argument extract_length (%s) mora biti pozitivan ili null."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The factor by which depreciation decreases."
msgstr "Faktor kojim se smanjuje amortizacija."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The field (%(fieldValue)s) must be one of %(dimRowDB)s or must be a number "
"between 1 and %s inclusive."
msgstr ""
"Polje (%(fieldValue)s) mora biti jedno od %(dimRowDB)s ili broj između 1 i "
"%s uključivo."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/list/list_functions.js:0
msgid "The field name should not be empty."
msgstr "Naziv polja ne bi smio biti prazan."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The file you are trying to copy is too large (>%sMB).\n"
"It will not be added to your OS clipboard.\n"
"You can download it directly instead."
msgstr ""
"Fajl koji pokušavate kopirati je prevelik (>%sMB).\n"
"Neće biti dodan u clipboard vašeg OS-a.\n"
"Možete ga umjesto toga preuzeti direktno."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The first and second arguments of [[FUNCTION_NAME]] must be non-empty "
"matrices."
msgstr "Prvi i drugi argument [[FUNCTION_NAME]] moraju biti neprazne matrice."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The first case to be checked against expression."
msgstr "Prvi slučaj koji se provjerava u odnosu na izraz."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The first column index of the columns to be returned."
msgstr "Indeks prve kolone od kolona koje se vraćaju."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The first condition to be evaluated. This can be a boolean, a number, an "
"array, or a reference to any of those."
msgstr ""
"Prvi uslov koji se evaluira. Ovo može biti boolean, broj, niz, ili referenca"
" na bilo šta od navedenog."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The first future cash flow."
msgstr "Prvi budući novčani tok."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The first matrix in the matrix multiplication operation."
msgstr "Prva matrica u operaciji množenja matrica."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The first number in the sequence"
msgstr "Prvi broj u nizu"

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The first number or range to add together."
msgstr "Prvi broj ili opseg za sabiranje."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The first number or range to calculate for the product."
msgstr "Prvi broj ili opseg za izračun proizvoda."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The first number to compare."
msgstr "Prvi broj za poređenje."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The first range to be appended."
msgstr "Prvi opseg koji se dodaje."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The first range to flatten."
msgstr "Prvi opseg za izravnavanje."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The first range whose entries will be multiplied with corresponding entries "
"in the other ranges."
msgstr ""
"Prvi opseg čiji će unosi biti pomnoženi s odgovarajućim unosima u drugim "
"opsezima."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The first row index of the rows to be returned."
msgstr "Indeks prvog reda od redova koji se vraćaju."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The first value or range in which to count the number of blanks."
msgstr "Prva vrijednost ili opseg u kojem se broji broj praznih ćelija."

