msgstr "Opseg koji sadrži skup klasa."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The range from which to return a result. The value returned corresponds to "
"the location where search_key is found in search_range. This range must be "
"only a single row or column and should not be used if using the "
"search_result_array method."
msgstr ""
"Opseg iz kojeg se vraća rezultat. Vraćena vrijednost odgovara lokaciji gdje "
"se search_key nalazi u search_range. Ovaj opseg mora biti samo jedan red ili"
" kolona i ne bi se trebao koristiti ako se koristi metoda "
"search_result_array."

#. module: spreadsheet
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
